narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Prof. Fuermann setquite an incredible reserve section, which covered pretty much all that was necessary to conduct my research for the semester. He was also very instructional in my finding additional resources outside of the prescribed syllabus; his knowledge of the subject matter and its literature is quite impressive.
